est facilities in the State of California. We can provide your business with recurring service for all of your communications, data, fire and sprinkler alarm testing, inspections, and monitoring needs.\r\n\r\nWe offer the most experienced and efficient technicians who have received training in all aspects of the installation process. Our technicians are provided with the latest tools and technology to improve the identification and repair of nearly all types of communications and low voltage needs.'),(417,105,'wpcf-service-list-item','Data, Phone and Fax Line Repair'),(418,105,'wpcf-service-list-item','Relocating and replacing existing equipment and lines'),(419,105,'wpcf-service-list-item','Diagnosis and Repair of fire panels, sound equipment, cameras, A/V, data, access control systems, CCTV, automation and more'),(420,105,'wpcf-service-list-item','System Network Integration'),(421,105,'wpcf-service-list-item','Fire Alarm Inspections with Reports'),(422,105,'_wpcf-service-list-item-sort-order','a:5:{i:0;i:417;i:1;i:418;i:2;i:419;i:3;i:420;i:4;i:421;}'),(423,14,'_wp_trash_meta_status','publish'),(424,14,'_wp_trash_meta_time','1424298242'),(425,107,'_wp_types_group_filters_association','any'),(426,107,'_wp_types_group_fields',',rw-location,rw-address,'),(427,107,'_wp_types_group_post_types',',rw-contact-us,'),(428,107,'_wp_types_group_terms','all'),(429,107,'_wp_types_group_admin_styles',''),(430,107,'_wp_types_group_templates',',contact.php,'),(431,107,'_wpcf_conditional_display','a:3:{s:10:\"custom_use\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"relation\";s:3:\"AND\";s:6:\"custom\";s:0:\"\";}'),(432,108,'_edit_last','1'),(433,108,'_edit_lock','1427498763:1'),(434,108,'wpcf-rw-location','Central Valley'),(435,108,'wpcf-rw-address','3582 W. Holland Ave'),(436,108,'wpcf-rw-address','Fresno, California 93722'),(437,108,'wpcf-rw-address','Phone: 559.271.9350'),(438,108,'wpcf-rw-address','FAX: 559.271.9354'),(439,108,'_wpcf-rw-address-sort-order','a:4:{i:0;i:435;i:1;i:436;i:2;i:437;i:3;i:438;}')