oltage systems. Specializing in system integration, we adhere to the highest quality standards to ensure customer satisfaction. As a full service company, we offer AUTOCAD design including the ability to perform 3D rendering. With a bonding capacity for large projects, low EMR, IIPP, and safety plans in place, Red Wave Communications is capable of handling all your residential and business design and integration needs with helpful and convenient customer service.\r\n\r\n<strong>About the Company\r\n</strong>Founded in 2002, Red Wave Communications Inc. has grown into a leading low voltage contractor throughout California, offering more than 30 years of combined experience and expertise in integration. Red Wave Communications is licensed by the California Contractors State License Board with A, B, C-7, and C-10 classifications. In addition, we are a State of California SBE organization, certified by the Department of General Services.','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-revision-v1','','','2015-03-27 18:23:00','2015-03-27 18:23:00','',4,'http://localhost:8080/4-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
